Joel DORRIS, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Donald McCORMICK, Defendant-Appellant. No. 30705. United States Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. June 8, 1971. H. O. Pemberton, Tallahassee, Fla., for defendant-appellant. Roy T. Rhodes, Tallahassee, Fla., for plaintiff-appellee.

Before GODBOLD, SIMPSON and CLARK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

Affirmed. See Local Rule 21.1

. See NLRB v. Amalgamated Clothing Workers of America, 5 Cir., 1970, 430 F.2d 966.
